      "comment": "MI PRECIOSO (2) has returned in good shape this preparation. Opened with a second at this track two starts back then got the job done by 1.3 lengths last time out over 1300m at this track. Must raise the bar but a big run is on the cards. ADICTIVA (4) followed an unplaced effort first-up two runs back with a second last start over 1300m at this track. Has her share of ability. Hard to beat in this suitable race. SALTO ETERNO (7) finished fifth two runs back then did well last start but found one better over 1600m at this track, beaten only a nose. Faces an easier assignment so he is perfectly placed to score. SEVEN SUMMITS (3) has not won for a long while. Last raced on April 11 when beaten 25 lengths into 14th at Hipodromo Chile over 1900m. Good enough on his day and can run a bold race.",
